"childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2757296194/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2757296194","tinyui":"/x/QgBZp","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2757296194","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2757296194/Archived+Initiatives","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2757296194"}},{"id":"3157852169","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/3157852169","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMzE1Nzg1MjE2OQ==","status":"current","title":"Comercio / Sucursal en Decodificación de QR","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":172688440},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/3157852169/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/3157852169/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/3157852169/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/3157852169/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/3157852169","tinyui":"/x/CQA5v","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=3157852169","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/3157852169/Comercio+Sucursal+en+Decodificaci+n+de+QR","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/3157852169"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"info\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"3296f4aa-9592-4ba6-a697-60f2f4474b5e\"><ac:rich-text-body><p>Esta iniciativa tiene que partir de la base de VisaQR en commerce-service por el MCC</p><p>El total para esta iniciativa son <strong>176hs</strong>. </p><p>Luego de terminado el desarrollo, se estiman 10hs m&aacute;s por semana, hasta el pase a producci&oacute;n</p></ac:rich-text-body></ac:structured-macro><table data-table-width=\"760\" data-layout=\"default\" ac:local-id=\"61e97148-f7e8-49be-aa93-45d307b66e3a\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 402.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 118.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 238.0px;\" /></colgroup><tbody><tr><th><p><strong>Tarea</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Estimaci&oacute;n</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Portal / Servicio</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td><p>Setup de Proyecto</p><p><em>Sujeto al responsable del desarrollo</em></p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">4</p></td><td><p>billing-proxy</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Integrarse con operaci&oacute;n get_commerce_branch de commerce-service para obtener la sucursal</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">36</p></td><td><p>billing-proxy</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Integrarse con operaci&oacute;n get_commerce de commerce-service para obtener el comercio</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">12</p></td><td><p>billing-proxy</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Agregar en el additional data de la operaci&oacute;n de decode_qr_decode el codigo de comercio, c&oacute;digo de sucursal y MCC</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">12</p></td><td><p>billing-proxy</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Agregar modulo de consumo de comercios/sucursales precargados en Redis</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">20</p></td><td><p>billing-proxy</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Eliminar l&oacute;gica de precarga de comercios/sucursales</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">8</p></td><td><p>selling-service</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Agregar modulo de precarga de comercios/sucursales en Redis con un job as&iacute;ncrono</p><p><em>Consultar comercios y sucursales en lotes.</em></p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">24</p></td><td><p>commerce-service</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Agregar l&oacute;gica para actualizaci&oacute;n de datos precargados en Redis ante la creaci&oacute;n/modificaci&oacute;n/eliminaci&oacute;n de comercios/sucursales</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">32</p></td><td><p>commerce-service</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Modificar configuraci&oacute;n para consumir comercios/sucursales del nuevo Redis</p><p>Quitar l&oacute;gica de guardado en caso de no encontrar el dato en Redis.</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">4</p></td><td><p>selling-service</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Modificar configuraci&oacute;n para consumir comercios/sucursales del nuevo Redis</p><p>Quitar l&oacute;gica de guardado en caso de no encontrar el dato en Redis.</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">4</p></td><td><p>external-commerce-service</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p>Desarrollo</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">156</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p /></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p>Gesti&oacute;n 15% (no afecta fecha entrega)</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">20</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p /></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#c0b6f2\"><p><strong>Total</strong></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#c0b6f2\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>176</strong></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#c0b6f2\"><p /></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffebe6\"><p>Soporte</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffebe6\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">10</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffebe6\"><p>por semana hasta pase a producci&oacute;n</p></td></tr></tbody></table>","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/3156836392"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":356},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/3156836